<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>心小跳塔羅 | 聆聽潛意識的聲音</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script>
        // 透過設定檔一鍵將原本的黃/灰色系，轉換為「玫瑰粉金」與「神秘暗紫」
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        yellow: {
                            400: '#fda4af',
                            500: '#fb7185',
                            600: '#f43f5e',
                            800: '#be123c',
                            900: '#881337',
                        },
                        gray: {
                            600: '#4d365e',
                            700: '#3f2b4f',
                            800: '#2d1f38',
                            900: '#1e1525',
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+TC:wght@300;400;600&family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap');

        :root {
            --gold: #fb7185; /* 玫瑰粉金 */
            --gold-light: #ffe4e6;
            --dark-bg: #1e1525; /* 神秘暗紫 */
            --dark-surface: #2d1f38;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--dark-bg);
            color: #e2e8f0;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        h1, h2, h3, h4, .serif {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
        }

        .glass-panel {
            background: rgba(45, 31, 56, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.2);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .gold-text { color: var(--gold); }
        .gold-glow { text-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.6); }

        .btn-gold {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fda4af 0%, #fb7185 100%);
            color: #1e1525;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn-gold:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.6);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-outline-gold {
            border: 1px solid var(--gold);
            color: var(--gold);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn-outline-gold:hover, .btn-outline-gold.active {
            background: rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.15);
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.3);
        }

        .fade-in-section {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            transition: opacity 0.8s ease-out, transform 0.8s ease-out;
            will-change: opacity, visibility;
        }
        .fade-in-section.is-visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: none;
        }

        .tarot-card-container { perspective: 1000px; cursor: pointer; }
        .tarot-card {
            width: 100%;
            padding-top: 170%;
            position: relative;
            transition: transform 0.6s;
            transform-style: preserve-3d;
        }
        .tarot-card.flipped { transform: rotateY(180deg); }
        
        .card-face {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            backface-visibility: hidden;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.5);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
            background-color: var(--dark-surface);
        }

        .card-back {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d1f38 0%, #1e1525 100%);
            background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, transparent 10px, rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.05) 10px, rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.05) 20px);
        }
        .card-back::after {
            content: '✧'; font-size: 2rem; color: var(--gold); opacity: 0.5;
        }

        .card-front {
            transform: rotateY(180deg);
            background: #fdfbf7;
        }
        
        .real-tarot-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--dark-bg); }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.5); border-radius: 3px; }
        
        .modal-overlay { backdrop-filter: blur(5px); }

        .stars {
            position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            /* 浪漫的暮光漸層背景 */
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #2a1635 0%, #110916 100%);
        }
        
        /* 扇形牌陣專用 CSS (優化觸控體驗與點擊精準度) */
        .fan-area {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: 180px; /* 適應更大的弧度 */
            margin-top: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            /* 防止意外的滾動或選取干擾 */
            user-select: none; 
            -webkit-user-select: none;
        }
        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .fan-area { height: 260px; margin-bottom: 5rem; }
        }
        .fan-card {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: calc(50% - 25px);
            width: 50px;
            height: 85px;
            transform-origin: center 280px; /* 更大的旋轉半徑 */
            transform: rotate(var(--rot));
            transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1), opacity 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            z-index: var(--idx);
            cursor: pointer;
            /* 關鍵：改善手機觸控回饋，取消預設的高光閃爍 */
            touch-action: manipulation;
            -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
        }
        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .fan-card {
                left: calc(50% - 35px);
                width: 70px;
                height: 115px;
                transform-origin: center 400px; 
            }
        }
        /* 關鍵修復：只有在真正的滑鼠設備上才套用 hover 位移，避免手機點擊時卡片逃跑導致點擊無效 */
        @media (hover: hover) and (pointer: fine) {
            .fan-card:hover {
                transform: rotate(var(--rot)) translateY(-25px) scale(1.1);
                z-index: 100 !important;
                box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(251,113,133,0.8);
            }
        }
        /* 手機與所有裝置通用的點擊瞬間回饋 */
        .fan-card:active {
            transform: rotate(var(--rot)) scale(1.05);
            z-index: 100 !important;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(251,113,133,0.8);
            filter: brightness(1.2);
        }
        
        .reading-content p {
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            line-height: 1.75;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        }
        .reading-content strong {
            color: #D4AF37;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="antialiased">

    <div class="stars"></div>

    <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 glass-panel py-4 transition-all duration-300 border-b-0 border-yellow-500/30" id="navbar">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 flex justify-between items-center">
            <div class="text-xl serif gold-text tracking-widest font-semibold flex items-center gap-2">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-heart-pulse"></i> 心小跳塔羅
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex gap-6 text-sm tracking-wide">
                <a href="#intro" class="hover:text-yellow-500 transition">關於占卜</a>
                <a href="#app-section" class="hover:text-yellow-500 transition">開始占卜</a>
                <a href="#tips" class="hover:text-yellow-500 transition">占卜指南</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section id="intro" class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center pt-20 px-4 relative">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center fade-in-section">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl serif mb-6 tracking-wider leading-tight">
                聆聽靈魂的聲音，<br>
                <span class="gold-text gold-glow">遇見未知的自己</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg md:text-xl mb-10 tracking-wide font-light leading-relaxed">
                這不是決定命運的判決，而是反映潛意識的鏡子。<br>
                基於百年傳承的偉特塔羅系統，我們為您準備了一個寧靜的空間。<br>
                深呼吸，在寧靜中尋找指引。
            </p>
            <a href="#app-section" class="inline-block btn-gold px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-lg tracking-wider shadow-lg">
                開啟靈魂對話 <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-down ml-2"></i>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 px-4 relative">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in-section">
                <h2 class="text-3xl serif gold-text mb-4">探索您的專屬指引</h2>
                <div class="h-0.5 w-16 bg-yellow-600 mx-auto"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="glass-panel p-8 rounded-xl text-center fade-in-section" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">
                    <div class="text-4xl gold-text mb-4"><i class="fa-solid fa-sun"></i></div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl serif mb-3 text-white">每日一抽</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">迎接新的一天前，抽取一張牌作為今日能量指引。系統會提供專屬的「具體行動建議」，讓占卜落實於生活。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="glass-panel p-8 rounded-xl text-center fade-in-section" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
                    <div class="text-4xl gold-text mb-4"><i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group"></i></div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl serif mb-3 text-white">深度問事</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">提供分類與客製化問題。支援 1張(核心)、3張(過去/現在/未來)、6張(深度視角)牌陣，尋找完整清晰的答案。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="glass-panel p-8 rounded-xl text-center fade-in-section" style="transition-delay: 300ms;">
                    <div class="text-4xl gold-text mb-4"><i class="fa-solid fa-book-journal-whills"></i></div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl serif mb-3 text-white">靈魂軌跡</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">自動記錄您的每一次抽牌歷史。您可以隨時回顧過去的指引，並收藏對您意義重大的占卜結果。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="tips" class="py-16 px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto glass-panel rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 fade-in-section">
            <h2 class="text-2xl serif gold-text mb-6 text-center">占卜前的小提醒</h2>
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
                <button onclick="openModal('modal-system')" class="btn-outline-gold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-eye"></i> 認識偉特系統</button>
                <button onclick="openModal('modal-question')" class="btn-outline-gold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i> 如何提出好問題？</button>
                <button onclick="openModal('modal-mindset')" class="btn-outline-gold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i> 抽牌時的心態</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="app-section" class="py-10 px-4 min-h-screen">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto fade-in-section">
            <div class="glass-panel rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-yellow-600/30">
                <div class="flex border-b border-gray-700/50">
                    <button onclick="switchTab('daily')" id="tab-daily" class="flex-1 py-4 text-center font-medium transition active-tab text-yellow-500 border-b-2 border-yellow-500 bg-white/5"><i class="fa-solid fa-sun mr-2"></i>每日一抽</button>
                    <button onclick="switchTab('reading')" id="tab-reading" class="flex-1 py-4 text-center font-medium text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-200 transition"><i class="fa-solid fa-star mr-2"></i>深度問事</button>
                    <button onclick="switchTab('history')" id="tab-history" class="flex-1 py-4 text-center font-medium text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-200 transition"><i class="fa-solid fa-clock-rotate-left mr-2"></i>歷史與收藏</button>
                </div>

                <div class="p-6 md:p-10 relative min-h-[500px]">
                    <!-- 面板：每日一抽 -->
                    <div id="panel-daily" class="tab-panel transition-all duration-500">
                        <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto" id="daily-setup">
                            <h2 class="text-3xl serif gold-text mb-4">今日能量指引</h2>
                            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">深呼吸三次，在心中默念：「請給我今日最需要的指引」，然後點擊下方抽牌。</p>
                            <div class="tarot-card-container w-48 mx-auto mb-8" onclick="drawDailyCard()">
                                <div class="tarot-card" id="daily-card-anim">
                                    <div class="card-face card-back"></div>
                                    <div class="card-face card-front" id="daily-card-front">
                                        <!-- 這裡將載入真實塔羅牌圖片 -->
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <button onclick="drawDailyCard()" class="btn-gold px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-lg tracking-wider w-full md:w-auto"><i class="fa-solid fa-hand-sparkles mr-2"></i> 抽取今日卡牌</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 面板：深度問事 -->
                    <div id="panel-reading" class="tab-panel hidden transition-all duration-500">
                        <div id="reading-setup" class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                            <h2 class="text-2xl serif gold-text mb-6 text-center">設定你的問題</h2>
                            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                                <div class="space-y-6">
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2">你想問哪方面的問題？</label>
                                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                                            <button type="button" class="category-btn btn-outline-gold active px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" onclick="selectCategory('love', this)">愛情與關係</button>
                                            <button type="button" class="category-btn btn-outline-gold px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" onclick="selectCategory('career', this)">事業與學業</button>
                                            <button type="button" class="category-btn btn-outline-gold px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" onclick="selectCategory('life', this)">生活與自我</button>
                                            <button type="button" class="category-btn btn-outline-gold px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" onclick="selectCategory('wealth', this)">財富與投資</button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2">具體的問題是？</label>
                                        <select id="suggested-questions" class="w-full bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg p-3 text-white mb-2 focus:border-yellow-500 outline-none transition" onchange="document.getElementById('custom-question').value = this.value">
                                            <option value="">-- 選擇一個建議問題，或在下方自己打 --</option>
                                        </select>
                                        <input type="text" id="custom-question" placeholder="例如：我該如何改善跟他的關係？" class="w-full bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg p-3 text-white focus:border-yellow-500 outline-none transition">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="space-y-6">
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2">你想抽幾張牌？</label>
                                        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2">
                                            <button type="button" class="spread-btn btn-outline-gold active px-2 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm flex flex-col items-center" onclick="selectSpread(1, this)"><span class="font-bold mb-1">單張牌</span><span class="text-xs opacity-70">簡單明確</span></button>
                                            <button type="button" class="spread-btn btn-outline-gold px-2 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm flex flex-col items-center" onclick="selectSpread(3, this)"><span class="font-bold mb-1">三張牌</span><span class="text-xs opacity-70">過去/現在/未來</span></button>
                                            <button type="button" class="spread-btn btn-outline-gold px-2 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm flex flex-col items-center" onclick="selectSpread(6, this)"><span class="font-bold mb-1">六張牌</span><span class="text-xs opacity-70">深度全方位</span></button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2">抽牌方式</label>
                                        <div class="flex gap-2">
                                            <button type="button" class="method-btn btn-outline-gold active px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm flex-1" onclick="selectMethod('auto', this)">交給系統抽</button>
                                            <button type="button" class="method-btn btn-outline-gold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm flex-1" onclick="selectMethod('manual', this)">我想自己選牌</button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mt-8 text-center">
                                <button onclick="startReading()" class="btn-gold px-10 py-3 rounded-full text-lg tracking-wider w-full md:w-auto shadow-lg hover:shadow-yellow-500/30">開始占卜</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- 手動抽牌區 -->
                        <div id="manual-draw-area" class="hidden flex flex-col items-center">
                            <h3 class="text-xl serif gold-text mb-2">放空思緒，憑直覺選出 <span id="cards-to-pick">3</span> 張牌吧</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6" id="current-question-display">問題：---</p>
                            <!-- 扇形牌陣容器 -->
                            <div id="deck-container" class="fan-area max-w-4xl mx-auto"></div>
                            <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 min-h-[120px] mt-4" id="selected-slots"></div>
                            <button id="btn-reveal" class="btn-gold px-8 py-3 rounded-full mt-8 hidden animate-pulse" onclick="revealCards()">揭曉牌面</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 面板：歷史紀錄 -->
                    <div id="panel-history" class="tab-panel hidden transition-all duration-500">
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
                            <h2 class="text-2xl serif gold-text">你的靈魂軌跡</h2>
                            <div class="flex gap-2 text-sm">
                                <button class="filter-btn text-yellow-500 underline" onclick="renderHistory('all')">全部紀錄</button>
                                <span class="text-gray-600">|</span>
                                <button class="filter-btn text-gray-400 hover:text-yellow-500 transition" onclick="renderHistory('favorites')">打星星的收藏</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div id="history-list" class="space-y-4 max-h-[60vh] overflow-y-auto pr-2"></div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 載入中動畫區 (新增顯示抽出的牌面) -->
                    <div id="loading-area" class="hidden flex-col items-center justify-center py-10 md:py-20 w-full">
                        <!-- 顯示剛抽出的塔羅牌陣 -->
                        <div id="loading-cards-display" class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mb-8 hidden w-full"></div>
                        
                        <div class="text-4xl text-yellow-500 mb-4 animate-bounce"><i class="fa-solid fa-heart-pulse"></i></div>
                        <p class="text-gray-400" id="loading-text">正在幫你洗牌，並與高我連結中...</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 共用結果顯示區 -->
                    <div id="result-area" class="hidden">
                        <button onclick="backToSetup()" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-2 transition"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i> 返回上一頁</button>
                        
                        <div class="text-center mb-8 relative">
                            <div id="ai-badge-container"></div>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl serif gold-text mb-2" id="res-title">占卜結果出來囉</h2>
                            <p class="text-gray-300 italic" id="res-question"></p>
                            <button id="btn-save-history" class="absolute right-0 top-0 text-gray-400 hover:text-yellow-500 transition text-2xl" onclick="toggleFavoriteCurrent()" title="收藏此紀錄">
                                <i class="fa-regular fa-star" id="fav-icon"></i>
                            </button>
                        </div>

                        <!-- 牌面展示區 (橫向排列) -->
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 md:gap-8 mb-10" id="res-cards-visual"></div>

                        <!-- 完整解析容器 -->
                        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto reading-content" id="res-detailed-content">
                            <!-- JS 動態插入單牌解析與整體總結 -->
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 text-center relative mt-10 border-t border-gray-800">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 fade-in-section">
            <h2 class="text-3xl serif mb-6 text-white">其實，答案一直都在你心裡</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-10 leading-relaxed font-light">
                不論抽到什麼牌，塔羅都只是一盞為你照亮前方的路燈。<br>
                真正能決定要怎麼走的，永遠是你自己。
            </p>
            <button onclick="openModal('modal-cta')" class="btn-gold px-10 py-4 rounded-full text-xl shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(212,175,55,0.4)] animate-pulse">
                點我領取宇宙給你的最後一句話 <i class="fa-solid fa-sparkles ml-2"></i>
            </button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="text-center py-6 text-gray-600 text-sm border-t border-gray-800 mt-10">
        <p>© 2026 心小跳塔羅. 讓靈魂休息的溫暖角落。</p>
    </footer>

